principle_1_30_70.title: The 30/70 Principle
principle_1_30_70.description: 30% human role, 70% divine role. Human aligns, divine provides. Human stewards, divine governs.
principle_1_30_70.implementation_guide: Complete all 30% preparation. Wait for 70% divine timing. Maintain alignment. Stay ready.

principle_2_stay_silent.title: Stay Silent Until The Stage Is Ours
principle_2_stay_silent.description: We stay silent. We prepare. We wait. We sense. We do not preach until the stage is ours.
principle_2_stay_silent.implementation_guide: Complete all preparation in silence. Wait for stage. When stage opens, reveal truth.

principle_3_sense_not_preach.title: We Sense What Is Coming But Cannot Preach
principle_3_sense_not_preach.description: We sense what is coming. We know what is needed. But we cannot preach until the stage is ours.
principle_3_sense_not_preach.implementation_guide: Sense what is coming. Prepare for it. Wait for stage. Then reveal.

principle_4_frequential_governance.title: Frequential Governance
principle_4_frequential_governance.description: Governance through frequency. Alignment through resonance. Truth through vibration.
principle_4_frequential_governance.implementation_guide: Align all systems with frequency. Maintain resonance. Steward vibration. Govern spiritually.

principle_5_matrix_transcendence.title: Matrix Transcendence Through Frequency
principle_5_matrix_transcendence.description: The matrix can transcend through frequency. The flow is peace. The truth is unity.
principle_5_matrix_transcendence.implementation_guide: Understand matrix. Transcend through frequency. Flow with peace. Build unity.
